headline: Q2 Earnings Roundup: Viatris (NASDAQ:VTRS) And The Rest Of The Generic Pharmaceuticals Segment
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how generic pharmaceuticals stocks fared in Q2, starting with Viatris (NASDAQ:VTRS).
